summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from Thomas H. Dempsey and Rowena R. Dempsey, his wife, to the City of Seattle, dated the 5th day of December, 1908, to certain portions of Lots three (3), four (4), five (5), six (6), seven (7), eight (8), nine (9), ten (10), eleven (11), twelve 912), thirteen (13), fourteen (14), fifteen (15), sixteen (16), seventeen (17), eighteen (18), nineteen (19), twenty (10), twenty-one (21), twenty-two (22), twenty-three (23) and twenty-four (24) Block thirteen (13) McKenzie & Dempsey's Lake Washington Addition to the City of Seattle.
